{"tid":2251770,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港首個國際黃色專業平台上線啦！！","createTime":"2020-10-21T04:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T06:48:59.000Z","uid":69472,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"845c6bd62c9dfc200a44e9eef5a849fd7078c199","tid":2251770,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:38:32.000Z","msg":"專業人士係咪好多收成期？<br />\nHKPN話比你地聽唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說有班人叫<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"teal\">HKPN（Hong Kong Professional Network）</span></span></strong><br />\n由喺美國及海外既香港人組成<br />\n想為香港既人提供專業既就業資訊<br />\n<br />\n無論係<strong><span class=\"purple\"><span class=\"large\">長途旅行既手足</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係<span class=\"green\"><strong><span class=\"large\">會移居美國既香港人</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至係<span class=\"pink\"><strong><span class=\"large\">仍喺香港、或其他國家、又有意投身唔同行業、想有一技之長既手足們</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要你係支持民主同自由兩大價值觀，<br />\nHKPN都好歡迎同你地展開激情對話！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uf57Tvi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuf57Tvi.jpg&h=e45d5405&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港手足冇一個係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論你身處喺邊，HKPN每2星期都有workshop介紹唔同行業入行既資訊；<br />\n<strong><span class=\"purple\">升業、就學</span></strong>都有專人去為你介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有唔同技能既<strong><span class=\"purple\">工作坊</span></strong>，coding, python，喺呢度都會搵到好勁既人去教你<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有<strong><span class=\"purple\">免費改resume既服務</span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺呢段日子，好多人都好無力，<br />\n如果你想充實下自己、學多樣技能，<br />\n可能入HKPN個facebook gp，<br />\n同呢班咁熱心既香港人一齊交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\"><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><p class=\"center\">Facebook lin:<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/groups/662107421185923\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fgroups%2F662107421185923&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=50b85aaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/groups/662107421185923</a></p></span></span>"},{"pid":"60aa196c4c418d1b96a18476dce9344b92e9f20c","tid":2251770,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:38:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2807a7fba4cdc139e0451a8e9426e5d0394c6e7e","tid":2251770,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:40:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127208003f7e4f142ddd0e22df11949112e56e9a","tid":2251770,"uid":178108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e97fe9c912b399e426c5a20dfc8ff3827b2e51cc","tid":2251770,"uid":178108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:40:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dfd900d387dd986e44a3765147bd2dfc68e4931f","tid":2251770,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"60aa196c4c418d1b96a18476dce9344b92e9f20c","tid":2251770,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:38:46.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im