dBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩我食開泥"},{"pid":"90c4ae221c7409f90ea535ce3318e57b69c1034c","tid":2251770,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f2073c2b461eeaf5cb3ac0f70567abe7970db0","tid":2251770,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:43:00.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9d39be486a03f6496236a4724499597cbaacaf","tid":2251770,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b360caa3aca8dc71d985feeb5ac435e90a2e2be7","tid":2251770,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d39f2f3210fc64158bb0ec452a3ebbd4cf83d40","tid":2251770,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"584d096e483bcd949f34b1ebd16aebd64dc8ec18","tid":2251770,"uid":206617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:47:44.000Z","msg":"得罪講句，個目標群體有咁明顯既政治傾向<br />\n點知你會唔會轉過頭就俾哂啲資料港共<br />\n又或者話，你地係呢方面做到一個點樣既 security 去保障我地？<br />\n你地真係可以做到一個好完整，仲要係黃既專業人士資料庫嫁喎，而呢個 database 都幾乎係一份名冊，你點保證佢唔落入港共手？"}]}